channel.title: What is the fun?
channel.description: Well, now i started thinking about making a RSPS, but what is actually the fun if there are others more funny RSPS's outta here? Why would they play mine? And what originality will there be if there are private servers with literally EVERYTHING?

item.title: What is the fun?
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

Is this even a help thread? But just because some other servers are higher accomplished than your own doesn’t mean you should stop trying. It’s good that you can shape a game you’ve played into something you want.

Just because there’s competition doesn’t mean you can’t win.
